The paper discusses the evaluation of deep neural network supervisors, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The supervisors are used to improve the robustness of DNNs, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and cybersecurity (cs.CR) applications. The paper also emphasizes the need for structured evaluation, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
